{"tid":2484820,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《世紀帝國 IV》將於今秋登陸 PC 平台，支援中文和中文語音","createTime":"2021-04-12T00:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T14:51:06.000Z","uid":51620,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"089bc840adc8dd8c62db0ed2fb79248f744c8816","tid":2484820,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T00:16:54.000Z","msg":"三年多前確認開發的微軟經典系列續作《世紀帝國 IV》（Age of Empire IV），終於在今天凌晨確認了上線時間，並公開了大量遊戲詳情。在剛剛結束的前瞻發表會上，官方宣佈該款作品將於今年秋季登陸 Windonws 10 和 Steam 商店，支援中文和中文語音，而且也會加入 Xbox Game Pass for PC 的遊戲陣容。在新放出的遊玩片段中，我們可以看到本作新加入的城牆攻防機制，玩家可控制士兵在牆上守城或是從牆下登牆進攻。<br />\n<br />\n在《世紀帝國 IV》中，包括中國、蒙古、英國以及新引入的德里蘇丹國等文明都會具備各自的特殊能力，<span class=\"red\">比如說蒙古就可以將建築整個「打包」然後重新設置營地</span>。另外微軟在今晨的活動中，還公佈了戰役模式裡四大史詩戰役中的一個 &mdash;「諾曼征服英格蘭」，對於喜歡歷史的玩家來說應該能在該模式中體驗到不少的樂趣<br />\n<br />\n除了公佈《世紀帝國 IV》的消息之外，微軟在這場發表會上也確認，《世紀帝國 II：決定版》將在今夏推出新 DLC「公爵的曙光」，而且在今年晚些時候還會增加新的合作遊玩模式。同時<span class=\"red\">《世紀帝國 III：決定版》會在 4 月 13 日更新美國文明，玩家在完成限時挑戰後便可免費獲得相關內容。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/age-of-empires-iv-preview-181255092.html?guccounter=1&amp;guce_referrer=aHR0cDovL20uZmFjZWJvb2suY29tLw&amp;guce_referrer_sig=AQAAACEv1gip6CB5QTi3OyFpRz6QrP0j56xP_yBbbFE6yZ1pXDd-07nBCPk9cHlM3W38FBvNjSlyWIh53sl8rkYlky7dx8BZ_bPFwIqKPyqPNWBWM9sAynWlsA6Gq-P39f2mlbGXD_VKFbUB6ipRsuA7SMXmUYQz1Phz25wib-yF_YIU&amp;fbclid=IwAR2SJ6CsoJEh1P8JWRD1BXA9MYa8S8e1n6QfrXg-eU42ANX6qCoBWmnG37A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2Fage-of-empires-iv-preview-181255092.html%3Fguccounter%3D1%26guce_referrer%3DaHR0cDovL20uZmFjZWJvb2suY29tLw%26guce_referrer_sig%3DAQAAACEv1gip6CB5QTi3OyFpRz6QrP0j56xP_yBbbFE6yZ1pXDd-07nBCPk9cHlM3W38FBvNjSlyWIh53sl8rkYlky7dx8BZ_bPFwIqKPyqPNWBWM9sAynWlsA6Gq-P39f2mlbGXD_VKFbUB6ipRsuA7SMXmUYQz1Phz25wib-yF_YIU%26fbclid%3DIwAR2SJ6CsoJEh1P8JWRD1BXA9MYa8S8e1n6QfrXg-eU42ANX6qCoBWmnG37A&d=WFG5iCHEkkmufTvr7zh8K%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=6dbe5077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/age-of-empires-iv-preview-181255092.html?guccounter=1&amp;guce_referrer=aHR0cDovL20uZmFjZWJvb2suY29tLw&amp;guce_referrer_sig=AQAAACEv1gip6CB5QTi3OyFpRz6QrP0j56xP_yBbbFE6yZ1pXDd-07nBCPk9cHlM3W38FBvNjSlyWIh53sl8rkYlky7dx8BZ_bPFwIqKPyqPNWBWM9sAynWlsA6Gq-P39f2mlbGXD_VKFbUB6ipRsuA7SMXmUYQz1Phz25wib-yF_YIU&amp;fbclid=IwAR2SJ6CsoJEh1P8JWRD1BXA9MYa8S8e1n6QfrXg-eU42ANX6qCoBWmnG37A</a>"},{"pid":"164e8dc6d13b5dd6bb787d0636a5366359253e72","tid":2484820,"uid":290145,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T00:31:05.000Z","msg":"唔睇好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />aoe2係不可跨越的牆"},{"pid":"b17a8bc0276007362febcda171c19b2610529b83","tid":2484820,"uid":185057,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"164e8dc6d13b5dd6bb787d0636a5366359253e72","tid":2484820,"uid":290145,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T00:31:05.000Z","msg":"唔睇好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />aoe2係不可跨越的牆"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T00:50:23.000Z","msg":"其實3代果種卡片模式唔差的,<br />\n只係2代太經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e54d13cf421d9aed5c7978063d8e8829d850cbb","tid":2484820,"uid":21279,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b17a8bc0276007362febcda171c19b2610529b83","tid":2484820,"uid":185057,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"164e8dc6d13b5dd6bb787d0636a5366359253e72","tid":2484820,"uid":290145,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T00:31:05.000Z","msg":"唔睇好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />aoe2係不可跨越的牆"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T00:50:23.000Z","msg":"其實3代果種卡片模式唔差的,<br />\n只係2代太經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T01:00:50.000Z","msg":"其實3好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebc18f08dec7601a7018c200f2210274a878a5e","tid":2484820,"uid":32934,"like":3,"dislik